<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="Arm-Circle">Arm Circle</h3>



<p><a href="https://www.endomondo.com/exercise/arm-circle" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Arm circles</a> are dynamic stretch that simultaneously warms up and lengthens the connective tissue of the shoulders. The gentle motion makes it great for lengthening the chest, shoulders, and rotator cuff. This is perfect for increasing shoulder mobility before a gym session or sport.</p>



